statements: SELECT * FROM properties;
SELECT property_id, address, price FROM properties;
SELECT property_id, price FROM properties WHERE bedrooms >= 4;
SELECT * FROM properties WHERE price < 100000;
SELECT address, bedrooms FROM properties WHERE price BETWEEN 50000 AND 150000;
SELECT * FROM properties WHERE bedrooms = 3 AND bathrooms = 2;
SELECT * FROM properties ORDER BY price DESC;

SELECT agent_id, email FROM agents WHERE phone IS NOT NULL;
SELECT agent_id, name FROM agents WHERE LENGTH(name) > 10;

SELECT AVG(price) AS avg_price FROM properties;
SELECT MAX(price) AS max_price FROM properties;
SELECT MIN(price) AS min_price FROM properties;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS property_count FROM properties;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT agent_id) AS agent_count FROM agents;
